org.eclipse.viatra.integration.mwe2.mwe2impl

Class Topic

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.viatra.integration.mwe2.mwe2impl.Topic
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ITopic

    public class Topic
extends java.lang.Object
implements ITopic
    Topics contain subscribing transformation steps and messages sent to these subscribers. Supports the addition of new subscribers and messages. To remove processed messages, transformation steps have to call the removeMessage method, this way ensuring that no message gets lost due a failure during processing This implementation can be used with most of the workflows that can be described using this library.
